import React from 'react';
import { Card, Button, Accordion, Form } from 'react-bootstrap'



export default () => {
  return (
    <Accordion>
      <Card >
        <Card.Header>
          <Accordion.Toggle as={Button} eventKey="0">
            Add a sandwich
          </Accordion.Toggle>
        </Card.Header>
        <Accordion.Collapse eventKey="0">
          <Card.Body>
            <Form>

            </Form>
          </Card.Body>
        </Accordion.Collapse>
      </Card>
    </Accordion>
  )
}
